description:
#Islam #Haqiqatjou #muslimskeptic 

Daniel Haqiqatjou reacts to hijabi university student who is frustrated with her schooling and with the idea of working at a tech company. She does not want to work and she also does not want to get married. Daniel analyzes this common feminist sentiment and discusses the factors that lead to the spread of this mindset in female youth, including Muslim women. Daniel also mentions how this mindset is destructive for future generations.

Original Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IBhLUyFQ4Ws
